Class AppointmentOutcome

java.lang.Object
Shared.AppointmentOutcome
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AppointmentOutcome extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the outcome of an appointment, including details of diagnosis, treatment, prescribed medicine, medicine collection status, and consultation notes.
